OL,6,FOn Friday, 24 January, Rose, who was
OL,7,Fon bail throughout her trial has been
OL,8,Fsentenced by Judge Mark Lucraft KC.
OL,10,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC said: "There are
OL,11,Fno words to describe this case other
OL,12,Fthan a deeply tragic one."
OL,14,FHe said the victims, aged three and
OL,15,Ffour, were left alone by their mother
OL,16,Fin an "unsafe" house when a fire broke
OL,17,Fout, likely caused by a tea light.
