OL,11,FSpeaking outside court, the boys'
OL,12,Ffamily said "justice" had been done
OL,13,Ffor them.
OL,15,FStep-grandmother Kerrie Hoath said the
OL,16,Fboys ` Bryson, Kyson, Logan and Leyton
OL,17,F` had been "cruelly taken away from
OL,18,Fus" by their mother.
