OL,6,FOf Rose, she said: "The disregard she
OL,7,Fshowed towards our boys has been
OL,8,Fechoed throughout this whole trial as
OL,9,Four family had to endure three years
OL,10,Fof lies, delays and false narratives.
OL,12,F"This time has been a nightmare and
OL,13,Fthe toll it's taken on our family
OL,14,Fcannot be overstated.
OL,16,F"We have heard speculation the fire
OL,17,Fwas caused by lights on a Christmas
OL,18,Ftree, false claims the boys were left
OL,19,Fwith a babysitter.
