OL,6,F"We thank the jury for seeing past
OL,7,Fthat and delivering us a true verdict."
OL,9,FRose and the children had been living
OL,10,Fin squalor, surrounded by rubbish and
OL,11,Fhuman excrement, before the tragedy.
OL,13,FProsecutor Kate Lumsdon KC had told
OL,14,Fthe court: "There was rubbish thickly
OL,15,Fspread throughout the house. The
OL,16,Ftoilet and the bath were full of
OL,17,Frubbish and could not be used. Buckets
OL,18,Fand pots were used as toilets instead."
