OL,6,FShe added: "I am afraid I will never
OL,7,Fbe able to forgive, on behalf of my
OL,8,Flittle ones. I will only say their
OL,9,Ffavourite word. Why?"
OL,11,FJurors were told that social worker
OL,12,FGeorgia Singh had raised concerns
OL,13,Fabout the family but the case was
OL,14,Fclosed three months before the fire.
OL,16,FPreviously, a health visitor had
OL,17,Fraised concerns about the family but
OL,18,Fthey were not followed up after she
OL,19,Fretired, jurors were told.
